The DGD2 LED Downlight Gimbal features the latest in performance LED Downlight technology, designed to create an attractive visual aesthetic that's incredibly easy to install. The high-performance DGD2 is Dimmable and features a 90 CRI rating, with an R9 value exceeding 50, making it one of the highest quality light fixtures on the market. Installation does NOT require a recessed housing or junction box, only a simple 2.125" diameter cut-out in the ceiling using the provided template. The elegantly designed fixture and off-board driver (included) allows for a more flexible installation and an increased lifespan thanks to the superior heat management system separated from the LED module itself. The DGD2 features adjustable spring-loaded retention tabs for a secure fit, eliminating the need for a recessed housing or junction box. Adding an adjustable, multi-directional light system to highlight artwork or architectural design features in your home just got easier. Freedom from having to use a housing or junction box allows this light to be installed in places others simply cannot. Available in Black, Nickel, Oil-Rubbed Bronze, and White. Choose from 2700K, 3000K, 4000K, or 5000K Color Temperatures. The DGD2 is Energy Star rated, Insulation Contact rated (IC-rated), Title 24 Compliant, Damp-Location rated, and protected by NICOR's 5-Year Limited Warranty.

entry.summary:

 6 in. Square Nickel Flat Panel LED Downlight in 3000K

Features
  • Includes LED Downlight Module, Off-Board Driver, and Nickel Faceplate
  • Includes 6.25-inch cut-out template
  • Installs directly into the ceiling. No housing or junction box needed.
  • 3000K Color Temperature

ATTRIBUTES
Model Number
DLE621203KSQNK
Product Title
DLE6 Series 6 in. Square Nickel Flat Panel LED Downlight in 3000K
UPC
767706164497



The DLE6 Edge Lit 6-inch Square LED Downlight creates an attractive visual aesthetic with a low profile that's incredibly easy to install. The edge-lit technology uses a reflective light guide panel that disperses light through a diffused lens, making it a practical, economical, and energy efficient solution for lighting your home or office. This high-performance downlight features 92 CRI, with an R9 value exceeding 50, making the DLE6 among the highest rated LED light fixtures in terms of light output quality. Installation no longer requires a recessed housing, but rather a simple 6.25" diameter cut-out in the ceiling using the provided template. The ultra-thin fixture depth (less than 1-inch) and off-board driver (included) allows for a more flexible installation and increased lifespan with superior heat management.
